<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HealthSync - Cadastro Concluído</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .agradecimento-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .agradecimento-container i {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .agradecimento-container h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        .agradecimento-container p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .back-to-login-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: var(--primary-gradient);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.3);
        }

        .back-to-login-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 255, 204, 0.4);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .agradecimento-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .agradecimento-container i {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .agradecimento-container h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .agradecimento-container p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .back-to-login-button {
                padding: 10px 20px;
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="agradecimento-container">
        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
        <h1>Cadastro Concluído!</h1>
        <p>Obrigado por se cadastrar no HealthSync. Agora você pode acessar sua conta e começar a cuidar da sua saúde!</p>
        <a href="/" class="back-to-login-button">Ir para o Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 